data.description: Mound Lake Estates Ph II, highly desirable gated subdivision. Level Lake Front lot. Man made finger lakes stocked and depth is 7 ft. Bill of Assurance and final plat available. Utilities available on site to include gas, water, electric, and community sewer treatment plant. Subdivision provides 150 ft. wide boat ramp access to Oxbow Lake. This subdivision is conveniently located to downtown NLR, LR, and the Air Force Base. Developer/Architectural Committee to approve house plans. SEE REMARKS.
